  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13067777/exclusive-discounts-with-inghams-lakes-and-mountains.jpg" alt="Exclusive Special Discounts" data-udi="umb://media/15ea0162a1bd45ccabd712f1d848a6c6" /></p>
<p>Book a <a data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">Lakes &amp; Mountains</a> holiday and you’ll not only get a great value summer holiday but you’ll also have access to fantastic discounts with some of our favourite brands. Receive discounted outdoor clothing and equipment with Cotswold Outdoors, special rates on Cicerone walking maps and guides, and discounted courier services.</p>
<p>Get these amazing benefits with your next Inghams Lakes &amp; Mountains holiday:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>15% Discount at Cotswold Outdoor</strong></li>
<li><strong>Save 20% with Cicerone</strong></li>
<li><strong>15% Discount with Pecksniff's</strong></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="page-title"><strong>15% Discount* at Cotswold Outdoor</strong></span></p>
<p><strong><img src="/media/13067776/cotswold-outdoor-discount-with-inghams-lakes-and-mountains.jpg" alt="Exclusive Discount with Cotswolds" data-udi="umb://media/689e23c995874b8988fa92bfa1491d0e" /></strong></p>
<p>Cotswold Outdoor has over four decades of experience providing an extensive range of clothing, equipment and accessories to the UK’s outdoor enthusiasts.</p>
<p>From walking boots and waterproof jackets to sun hats and water bottles, Cotswold Outdoors is the ideal place to purchase the outdoor clothing and equipment you need for your Lakes &amp; Mountains holiday.</p>
<p>Book your summer holiday with Inghams today, and we’ll send you a voucher code to use in store and online.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.cotswoldoutdoor.com/" target="_blank" title="Cotswold Outdoor"><strong>Read more  &gt;</strong></a></p>
