<tr>
<td width="auto" height="20" align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #f26419; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong><a style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">Find your Inghams Summer holiday</a></strong></span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="page-title"><strong>Save 20% on Cicerone Guides</strong></span></p>
<p><img src="/media/13067778/cicerone-discount-with-inghams-lakes-and-mountains.jpg" alt="Inghams Discount with Cicerone" data-udi="umb://media/cabd60afa8d24220ad72ed4aefadd4c1" /></p>
<p>At Inghams, we’re big fans of Cicerone’s extensive range of walking guides, which have been helping us explore the Lakes &amp; Mountains for nearly 50 years.</p>
<p>Cicerone publish over 350 different walking guidebooks, many providing detailed information on some of our favourite Lakes &amp; Mountains destinations.</p>
<p>Book your summer holiday with Inghams today, and we’ll send you a voucher code to use.</p>
<p><br /><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.cicerone.co.uk/" target="_blank" title="Cicerone Walking Guides"><strong>View full range of walking guides &gt;</strong></a></p>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 20px; width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td width="auto" height="20" align="center" valign="middle" style="background-color: #f26419; border-top-left-radius: 4px; border-bottom-left-radius: 4px; border-top-right-radius: 4px; border-bottom-right-radius: 4px; background-clip: padding-box; padding-left: 18px; padding-right: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><strong><a style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none;" data-udi="umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416" href="/{localLink:umb://document/96a3e4d143704d3e93793368e4fc0416}" title="Lakes &amp; Mountains Holidays">Find your Inghams Summer holiday</a></strong></span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="page-title"><strong>15% Discount with Pecksniff’s</strong></span></p>
<p>Pecksniff’s have been creating inspiring products from their Brighton boutique for over 30 years. They are the official provider of toiletries to our Lakes &amp; Mountains Chalet Hotels. Pecksniff’s inspiring fragrances are created through a mixture of master perfumery skills and innovative cosmetic science.</p>
<p>Their bespoke collection of fragrances, body and hair care products for both men and women are now available to Inghams guests with an exclusive 15% discount.</p>
<p>Book your summer holiday with Inghams today, and we’ll send you a voucher code to use.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://www.pecksniffs.com/" target="_blank" title="Pecksniff's Fragrances"><strong>Read more &gt;</strong></a></p>
<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="tablet-button" style="height: 20px; width: 300px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
