</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p>*Cotswold Outdoor discount is only valid for customers signed up to the free Explore More benefits scheme. Full T&amp;Cs apply. Not to be used in conjunction with any other oﬀer or discount. Selected lines are exempt. Maximum 10% discount on bikes. Only valid upon production of your booking confirmation in-store or use of valid discount code online. </p>]]></bodyText>
